title: Auto gordian knot 2.2
description:
This genius piece of software.
 AGK makes it possible to convert a full length movie into a 175 MB file. Depending on the type of quality you want, you can go as high as a 2 GB file. If you want to fit the movie onto a CD for instance, you can select for it to be converted to a 700 MB file (cd size). The quality on a 700 MB file is a little better than VHS quality (which is GREAT).
